data.description: Fabulous single family home on prime lot in desired South Mountain location! Charming curb appeal & mountain views greet you upon arrival at this lovingly cared for home nestled in picturesque subdivision. Inviting front entry walks into open living area with abundant natural light & vaulted ceilings. Practical floor plan allows for dedicated dining area & features large kitchen with walk in pantry. Set up perfectly for entertaining & indoor/outdoor lifestyle with direct access off living area to expansive back patio. Enormous backyard offers endless possibilities & is elevated for privacy. Primary bedroom has spacious feel with high ceilings, bay window, walk-in closet, & full bathroom. Bonuses include 2 car garage, RV gate, new AC, large laundry area & plenty of storage. Great location surrounded by mountains, trails, shopping, dining, golf and quick freeway access.
